(156, 1, '2023-03-24 21:44:12', '2023-03-24 21:44:12', '<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","width":900,"height":506,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img src="https://www.anscommerce.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/%E2%80%A2-Fairhill-Market-%E2%80%A2-1.png" alt="" width="900" height="506"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Is free shipping good for your bussines?</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Offering free shipping on your online shop can be a powerful marketing tool that can benefit both your customers and your business. Here are some reasons why:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>It Attracts Customers</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Customers love free shipping. It''s a great way to incentivize them to make a purchase. By offering free shipping, you can attract more customers to your online shop, increasing the chances of making a sale.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true,"start":2} -->\n<ol start="2"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>It Increases Order Value</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Offering free shipping can also increase your average order value. Customers are more likely to add items to their cart to reach the minimum purchase threshold for free shipping. This can result in larger orders and increased revenue for your business.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true,"start":3} -->\n<ol start="3"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>It Improves Customer Satisfaction</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Shipping costs can be a major pain point for customers. By offering free shipping, you can improve customer satisfaction and reduce cart abandonment rates. Customers are more likely to complete their purchase when they don''t have to worry about additional shipping costs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true,"start":4} -->\n<ol start="4"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>It Can Increase Repeat Business</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Customers are more likely to return to your online shop if they have had a positive experience. Offering free shipping can be a way to make a positive impression on your customers, increasing the likelihood that they will return for future purchases.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In conclusion, offering free shipping can be a powerful marketing tool for your online shop. It can attract more customers, increase order value, improve customer satisfaction, and increase repeat business. Consider offering free shipping on your online shop to see these benefits for yourself.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The Benefits of Offering Free Shipping on Your Online Shop', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-benefits-of-offering-free-shipping-on-your-online-shop', '', '', '2023-03-24 22:14:23', '2023-03-24 22:14:23', '', 0, 'http://localhost/Projects/Wordpress/shop-wp-bs/?p=156', 0, 'post', '', 0),
