(201, 1, '2023-03-26 09:55:21', '2023-03-26 09:55:21', '<strong>Features</strong>\r\n<table class="data-table" style="height: 367px;" width="390">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="spec-name">Mark</td>\r\n<td class="spec-value">Apple</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="spec-name">Processor</td>\r\n<td class="spec-value">Apple M2</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="spec-name">Video Card</td>\r\n<td class="spec-value">M2 (8-Core)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="spec-name">Storage Type</td>\r\n<td class="spec-value">SSD</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="spec-name">Internal working memory (RAM)</td>\r\n<td class="spec-value">8GB</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="spec-name">Display Type</td>\r\n<td class="spec-value">IPS (In-Plane Switching)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'APPLE MacBook Air 13.6 (2022) - Middernacht M2 8-Core GPU 8GB 256GB', 'The thin and powerful MacBook Air is a 13-inch laptop with a Retina display and a powerful Apple M2 chip. The screen provides unprecedented sharpness and accurate color reproduction, so you can enjoy your favorite movies, series or photos. Thanks to the Apple M2 chip, MacBook Air graphics are sharper and smoother than ever before. Thanks to the 8-core processor, this chip provides high performance and smooth, sharp graphics. Thus, you can easily work with various demanding programs, for example, for photo and video editing. The laptop also has a MagSafe 3 charging port and 2 Thunderbolt 4 ports, so you can easily connect peripherals.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'apple-macbook-air-13-6-2022-middernacht-m2-8-core-gpu-8gb-256gb', '', '', '2023-03-26 10:03:33', '2023-03-26 10:03:33', '', 0, 'http://localhost/Projects/Wordpress/shop-wp-bs/?post_type=product&#038;p=201', 0, 'product', '', 0),
